content.rendered:
Directed by Venky Kudumula.

Written by Vishwa Karun. Venky Kudumula. Venky Kudumula. Venky Kudumula.

Cast Naga Shaurya(Hari). Rashmika Mandanna(L. Karthika). Achyuth Kumar(Kesavulu). Mime Gopi(Veeramuthu). V.K. Naresh(Hari’s father). Pragathi(Hari’s mother). Harsha Chemudu(Tamilian (as Viva Harsha)). Satya(Sathya). Raghu Babu(Principal Paramathma). Vennela Kishore(Revenge Param). Praveen(Auto Driver Bose). Krishna Murali Posani(Lecturer). Motta Rajendran(Veeramuthu). Inturi Vasu(Nalla Seenu). Swapnika(Raji, Karthika’s friend). Venu Gopal(Venugopal) .Md Ariful Islam.Jeeva.Mico Nagaraj. Ferdous Nir(Rocky). Saifur Rahman Noyon(Kartik). Saifur Rahman(Kartik). Md Saykat Ahmed Rayhan(Raj).Pammi Sai.Sivannarayana.Sudharshan

Language Telugu.

Producers Aneesh Dev. Usha Mulpuri.

Production Ira Creations.
